column3:
To speak to new consumer needs that would have emerged from the COVID-19 outbreak, we focus on the Shell Advance AX7 product, highlighting the fuel economy benefit to communicate eventual cost savings. 

This ZIP contains the .ai files for the Shell Advance COVID-19 Recovery Phase AX7 Consumer Poster.
